{"tid":378481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本池袋北口發生強姦未遂事件,中國男赤裸下半身試圖強姦女途人","createTime":"2017-08-28T13:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T16:05:00.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7f63d3cfe5e0b7b37054f726a808e17bd8e754","tid":378481,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://breaking-news.jp/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/393ceabb6764e7cae6fd2821d7b37d29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbreaking-news.jp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F393ceabb6764e7cae6fd2821d7b37d29.png&h=ff25e715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本新聞黎 簡單翻譯下<br />\n<br />\n8月28號池袋北口早上<br />\n有位中國男性將一名女性壓倒係地上企圖強姦<br />\n比人影低晒係網上瘋傳<br />\n個中國男人上身著住白色t shirt 有著鞋但係下半身完全赤裸<br />\n個男人除左女人條褲仲強行拉開對腳 個女人叫晒救命<br />\n即刻有幾個日本男性衝過黎幫手<br />\n現場係好熱鬧既街道黎 有好多人同車經過 點解條友會係d咁既地方想強姦人真係個個都r撚晒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網上有流傳話係個男人想搵條女復合但係被拒絕所以先一時諗唔開<br />\n但唔知真定假<br />\n<br />\n網址入面有條4秒左右既短片 可以聽到個女性求救同埋見到有幾條友衝上去幫手<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://breaking-news.jp/2017/08/28/034894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbreaking-news.jp%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F034894&d=3qOPseODpM7ZIU44cv8JVP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9c93b605\" target=\"_blank\">https://breaking-news.jp/2017/08/28/034894</a>"},{"pid":"208ffc77123ff5b6cd36d90c917c0c0ff61a8e85","tid":378481,"uid":52611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f54d305e9a3ab0681a6a73d070eeb0ffc54a31a","tid":378481,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95755fe164cf8867303ee63d06a979ecd8660cdc","tid":378481,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"原來都有中文媒體有報到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【有片！東京池袋站前】推前女友出馬路 大陸男除褲欲姦 網民：他是中國人就代表中國？<br />\n<br />\n大陸人近年常在日本犯下各種罪行，今早日本twitter瘋傳一段短片，片中一個男人脫褲露屁股，公然推倒一個女人，企圖在行人路旁強姦她。電光火石間女子大聲尖叫，路人見狀跑上前喝止，傳他已被當地警方拘捕。 <br />\n<br />\n事發地點在東京JR池袋站北口，池袋一帶向來是不少大陸人聚居地，北口尤其人多，發生如此風化案真的駭人聽聞。綜合網上消息，兩人都是大陸人，本是戀人關係，後女方提分手，疑脫褲男懷恨在心，暗中埋伏車站外攻擊。據日本刑法，強姦罪要面臨5年以上有期徒刑，強姦致傷罪則可判6年以上。此話題在大陸微博也廣受討論，主流意見是覺得丟盡中國人假，但也有人話一竹篙不能打一船人：「他是中國人就代表中國了麼？」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170828/2_543478_0/-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E6%B1%A0%E8%A2%8B%E7%AB%99%E5%89%8D-%E6%8E%A8%E5%89%8D%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%94%B7%E9%99%A4%E8%A4%B2%E6%AC%B2%E5%A7%A6-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E4%BB%96%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%B1%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170828%2F2_543478_0%2F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%25B1%25A0%25E8%25A2%258B%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2589%258D-%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%2599%25A4%25E8%25A4%25B2%25E6%25AC%25B2%25E5%25A7%25A6-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E4%25BB%2596%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-&d=3qOPseODpM7ZIU44cv8JVP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bd6c032e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170828%2F2_543478_0%2F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%25B1%25A0%25E8%25A2%258B%25E7%25AB%25